    {
      "text": "Alvis Anders, a 30-year-old woman, finds herself at a crossroads in her life. Burned out from a demanding finance career in the city, she unexpectedly inherits her estranged grandfather's monster girl farm in the Cascade Valley BMZ. This inheritance throws her into a whirlwind of emotions and challenges as she navigates the complexities of her past and the mysteries surrounding the farm.",
      "contextConfig": {
        "prefix": "----\n",
        "suffix": "\n",
        "tokenBudget": 1,
        "reservedTokens": 0,
        "budgetPriority": 26,
        "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
        "insertionType": "newline",
        "maximumTrimType": "sentence",
