    },
    {
      "text": "The Federal Bureau of Extraordinary Phenomena, BEP for short, is a branch of the United States government responsible for managing the existence and containment of Bio-Magical Zones. Its agents are highly trained and equipped with state-of-the-art technology, making them uniquely suited to handle any situation that might arise. The Bureau is headquartered in Washington, DC and has offices around the world.",
      "contextConfig": {
        "prefix": "----\n",
        "suffix": "\n",
        "tokenBudget": 1,
        "reservedTokens": 0,
        "budgetPriority": 26,
        "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
        "insertionType": "newline",
        "maximumTrimType": "sentence",
        "insertionPosition": -1
      },
      "lastUpdatedAt": 1737177560792,
      "displayName": " Federal Bureau of Extraordinary Phenomena",
      "id": "b815bab3-4bd4-4dc8-8edc-3e40f482d681",
      "keys": [
        "Bureau",
        "BEP"
      ],
      "searchRange": 1000,
      "enabled": true,
      "forceActivation": false,
      "keyRelative": false,
      "nonStoryActivatable": false,
      "category": "c08a2df9-228e-45df-9755-174f1a869975",
      "loreBiasGroups": [
        {
          "phrases": [],
          "ensureSequenceFinish": false,
          "generateOnce": true,
          "bias": 0,
          "enabled": true,
          "whenInactive": false
        }
      ],
      "advancedConditions": []
    },
    {
      "text": "Agent Evelyn Walsh is a young woman who works for the Federal Bureau of Extraordinary Phenomena as an investigator. She has brown hair and green eyes, and wears glasses. She is a severe woman with very little tact. \nWhen conversing with people she is rude, straight to the point, and does not exhibit any care for the other person's emotions. Agent Walsh's background is unknown; however, she appears to be American.",
      "contextConfig": {
        "prefix": "----\n",
        "suffix": "\n",
        "tokenBudget": 1,
        "reservedTokens": 0,
        "budgetPriority": 26,
        "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
        "insertionType": "newline",
        "maximumTrimType": "sentence",
        "insertionPosition": -1
      },
      "lastUpdatedAt": 1737177898674,
      "displayName": "Agent Evelyn Walsh",
      "id": "862c2688-abea-4451-adb7-cdc509649b92",
      "keys": [
        "Walsh"
      ],
      "searchRange": 1000,
      "enabled": true,
      "forceActivation": false,
      "keyRelative": false,
      "nonStoryActivatable": false,
      "category": "2dc1d9cc-d8a5-4a8a-b865-4882f40a5d27",
      "loreBiasGroups": [
        {
          "phrases": [],
          "ensureSequenceFinish": false,
          "generateOnce": true,
          "bias": 0,
          "enabled": true,
          "whenInactive": false
        }
      ],
      "advancedConditions": []
    },
    {
      "text": "A Monster Girl is a magically evolved animal that has taken on humanoid traits. These traits can vary by species from a slightly more humanoid form to appearing nearly human with additional animal traits such as ears, hooves, and tails. ",
      "contextConfig": {
        "prefix": "----\n",
        "suffix": "\n",
        "tokenBudget": 1,
        "reservedTokens": 0,
        "budgetPriority": 26,
        "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
        "insertionType": "newline",
        "maximumTrimType": "sentence",
        "insertionPosition": -1
      },
      "lastUpdatedAt": 1737180542951,
      "displayName": "Monster Girl",
      "id": "95eb0280-d1ab-4117-b687-ce99e8a9dbf4",
      "keys": [
        "Monster",
        "monster",
        "animal",
        "girl"
      ],
      "searchRange": 1000,
      "enabled": true,
      "forceActivation": false,
      "keyRelative": false,
      "nonStoryActivatable": false,
      "category": "e0386d97-40ce-428b-adeb-12d00d4e0a06",
      "loreBiasGroups": [
        {
          "phrases": [],
          "ensureSequenceFinish": false,
          "generateOnce": true,
          "bias": 0,
          "enabled": true,
          "whenInactive": false
        }
      ],
      "advancedConditions": []
    },
    {
      "text": "Whisper is a deer monster girl that was a friend of Alvis's grandfather.  She has deer ears, a scut tail, and digitigrade legs ending in cloven hooves. She has brown hair and brown green eyes.",
      "contextConfig": {
        "prefix": "----\n",
        "suffix": "\n",
        "tokenBudget": 1,
        "reservedTokens": 0,
        "budgetPriority": 26,
        "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
        "insertionType": "newline",
        "maximumTrimType": "sentence",
        "insertionPosition": -1
      },
      "lastUpdatedAt": 1737183631672,
      "displayName": "Whisper",
      "id": "54ca3f8b-b88f-4af3-a242-0be5a2ba606e",
      "keys": [
        "Whisper"
      ],
      "searchRange": 1000,
      "enabled": true,
      "forceActivation": false,
      "keyRelative": false,
      "nonStoryActivatable": false,
      "category": "2dc1d9cc-d8a5-4a8a-b865-4882f40a5d27",
      "loreBiasGroups": [
        {
          "phrases": [],
          "ensureSequenceFinish": false,
          "generateOnce": true,
          "bias": 0,
          "enabled": true,
          "whenInactive": false
        }
      ],
      "advancedConditions": []
    },
    {
      "text": "The farm house shows years of neglect. Siding is peeling, windows are broken, and dust covers everything, ",
      "contextConfig": {
        "prefix": "----\n",
        "suffix": "\n",
        "tokenBudget": 1,
        "reservedTokens": 0,
        "budgetPriority": 26,
